title: #198: Amy Phillips One on One?David?!
description:
Ronnie Karam (TrashTalkTV) is without partner Ben Mandelker this week, so it?s time to cheat with amazing comics! First up is the hilarious and incomparable Amy Phillips (@amyphillips_) of Bravo TV Real Housewives Impersonation fame. She?s hilarious, and talking about Real Housewives of Orange County is a trip straight to the looney bin. We also did a Book Club reading of RHOMiami Lea Black?s book, Red Carpets and White Lies! Come on in!
Subscribe at http://www.patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens for bonus episodes, ringtones, and live group video chat parties.
